{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1097/comments/1982475.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:None..None?path=gazebo%2Fphysics%2Fode%2FODEJoint.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1097/_/diff#comment-1982475"}}, "parent": {"id": 1981092, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1097/comments/1981092.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1097/_/diff#comment-1981092"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1097, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1097.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1097"}}, "title": "fix issue #1138 for default (gazebo 4.0 candidate)"}, "content": {"raw": "I agree with @iche033 ; I don't like repeated code. What if we made a protected method called `Joint::SetPositionMaximal` that is called by ODEJoint and BulletJoint? This way, it's not part of the public API, but it can be shared between the two physics engines. Also, since it's not virtual, I think it won't impact ABI.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I agree with @iche033 ; I don't like repeated code. What if we made a protected method called <code>Joint::SetPositionMaximal</code> that is called by ODEJoint and BulletJoint? This way, it's not part of the public API, but it can be shared between the two physics engines. Also, since it's not virtual, I think it won't impact ABI.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2014-05-27T19:55:51.665478+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "outdated": false, "path": "gazebo/physics/ode/ODEJoint.cc"}, "updated_on": "2014-05-27T19:55:51.676550+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 1982475}